### =================
### WORKOUT CONTROLLER TESTS
### =================

### 1. Create a new workout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workouts
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutName": "Morning HIIT",
  "workoutDescription": "High intensity interval training for morning energy",
  "workoutCategory": "CARDIO",
  "isCardio": true,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/hiit-image.jpg"
}

### 2. Get all workouts for user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workouts
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 3. Get specific workout by ID (replace {id} with actual workout ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workouts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 4. Update a workout (replace {id} with actual workout ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/workouts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutName": "Updated Morning HIIT",
  "workoutDescription": "Updated high intensity interval training",
  "workoutCategory": "CARDIO",
  "isCardio": true,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/updated-hiit-image.jpg"
}

### 5. Delete a workout (replace {id} with actual workout ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/workouts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### =================
### WORKOUT LOG CONTROLLER TESTS
### =================

### 6. Create a workout log entry
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workout-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutId": 1,
  "date": "2024-06-05",
  "notes": "Great workout session, felt energized"
}

### 7. Get all workout logs for user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workout-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 8. Get workout logs by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workout-logs?startDate=2024-06-01&endDate=2024-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 9. Get specific workout log by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workout-logs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 10. Update a workout log
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/workout-logs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutId": 1,
  "date": "2024-06-05",
  "notes": "Updated notes: Excellent workout, increased intensity"
}

### 11. Delete a workout log
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/workout-logs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}